---
title: Savory Mixed Mushroom Bowl with Farro and Almonds
description: Savoury mushrooms are tossed in cornstarch and pan-fried for a lovely crisp exterior.  Tender farro, sweet greens, creamy avocado and a punchy mustard dressing fill out the rest of the bowl. Sprinkle it all with toasted almonds for a finishing flourish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bol-de-champignons-02f88ce0.jpg
